- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper deals with improving distributed word representations. 
- cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is a possible category as the paper evaluates the performance of the proposed method on word similarity and relatedness datasets. 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is a less likely category, but still possible as the paper discusses normalization methods such as cosine similarity and KL-divergence, which are commonly used in computer vision tasks.
